## Surface layers

Product UX: **`.cursor/rules/rimvio-jobs-layers.mdc`**

- `/` Feed (Shorts) · `/stack` one-card focus · `/now` Share landing · `/inbox` deep feed
- Share → `/now` → Done (do not dump into scroll feed)

## UI vocabulary

- Action Card, Prefetch, Shimmer — allowed
- User copy: Rimvio / 림비오 — not Blink, not Silent Ghost
- Avoid internal infra terms in user-facing copy

## File conventions

- `components/action-card.tsx` — primary interaction surface
- `lib/enrichers/` — domain enrichers + registry
- `lib/action-chat/orchestrator/` — chat routing pipeline
- `lib/supabase/` — client, server, middleware
- `app/share/` — Share Target bridge

